{"title":"彩色小河","authors":["曹复"],"dates":[{"year":1978,"month":9,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"彩色小河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曹复"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛是一条彩色的小河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪耀着奇异的光波，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"排队买书的人群，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在长街上缓缓地流着……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从知识的海洋里流过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向着理想的明天汇合，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"舒心地唱着，豪放地笑着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赞美春天里的新生活！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流进焦渴的心田，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流进待开发的沙漠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流进孩子们幻想的世界，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流进青年人求知的心窝。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滋润着绿苗棵棵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浇灌出红花朵朵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带给大地勃勃生机，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国哟满园春色……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}